{
  "stem": "3380.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had an advantage that we remained in our own house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I mean, for the people what they used to live, let's say, in the better locations, or in a different locations, they were pushed in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, that-- they lost their homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were only given two days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had to share with them the apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't even give us a break that we should take in the people what we know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just, within two days, they had to move.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had to pack in people wherever they could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was actually generated by the Germans, that it should be friction between ourselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that-- this created frictions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, the-- the people that were in the ghetto now, were they just from your community of Lask?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or were they--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So far, except there are-- there were certain people that they came from other towns, because they used to make judenrein certain areas not far from us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some often came to our town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was-- that used to be-- belonged to Germany before the war-- I mean, before the-- the first world war, like Poznan, Bydgoszcz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, a lots of ghettos that feel they had family in Lask, they came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lots of people came to our ghettos, all right, by themself-- not forced in, but they came voluntarily.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, they came because the-- their cities had to be wiped out of Jews, you know-- so ended up going someplace.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to ship 'em to Lublin, in the vicinity-- so ended up going there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if they have families, relative in our town, they came to Lask.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poznan, Bydgoszcz--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Kalisz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poznan is P-A-- oh-- P-O-S-N-A-N-- Poznan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a big-- big city in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
